title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 30 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 30 2021
description:
EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, interviews Mark Morgan, Trump/Obama head of Customs and Border Protection. A look at the racism behind welcoming a flood of foreign nationals to break into our nation illegally. 


Michael Berry, chats with Bob Unanue, CEO of Goya Foods, who discusses the supply chain, inflation, and the "buycott" that defeated the left's boycott after he dared say a kind word about Trump. 


Journalist Jordan Schachtel on the FDA failing to actually approve any covid vaccine. 

Michael Berry, welcomes Jack Posobiec to dissect the Ghislaine Maxwell guilty verdict matters.
